<plot>One of the series of shorts featuring the MacDougall Alley Kids, where their benefactor, Miss Fortune, takes them to the home of Farmer and Mrs. Brown, after writing them she is bringing the kids from her Sunday School class to visit their farm. The Browns are enthused over the prospect of entertaining "the little angels." The Browns, of course, have never met the kids from MacDougall's Alley.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?411128</url></doc>
